DESCRIPTION
This is an ATM style program that can be used within the terminal with an interface asking for checking balance, depositing and withdrawing money and error messages if a minus number is entered or the amount being withdraw exceeds the balance.
INSTRUCTIONS
first open terminal/commmand line and navigate to the file folder where the script is saved.
then type in the command line/Terminal "node ATM.js"
this will start the ATM simulator and you will be prompted to choose an option.

PLease try it and see what happens when you run out of balance!

Enjoy!
